{
  "script_id": "gram-schmidt",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "gram-schmidt",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gram-schmidt/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.77,
      "size": 44352,
      "text": "我们常常拿到一组线性无关的向量，它们能张成空间，却彼此歪斜、不垂直。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gram-schmidt",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gram-schmidt/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36720,
      "text": "很多计算，比如求投影、做分解，都希望基是互相垂直的。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gram-schmidt",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gram-schmidt/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.82,
      "size": 45072,
      "text": "施密特正交化就是一台机器，把任意一组基改造成互相垂直的标准正交基。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gram-schmidt",
      "section_id": "projection",
      "line_id": "proj-1",
      "filename": "projection-proj-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gram-schmidt/xiaoxiao/projection-proj-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.71,
      "size": 43344,
      "text": "先看投影。一个向量在另一个向量方向上的影子，就是它的正交投影。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gram-schmidt",
      "section_id": "projection",
      "line_id": "proj-2",
      "filename": "projection-proj-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gram-schmidt/xiaoxiao/projection-proj-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.5,
      "size": 40032,
      "text": "投影等于两向量的点积，除以被投影向量的模长平方，再乘以那个向量。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gram-schmidt",
      "section_id": "projection",
      "line_id": "proj-3",
      "filename": "projection-proj-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gram-schmidt/xiaoxiao/projection-proj-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.25,
      "size": 36000,
      "text": "把原向量减去这个投影，剩下的部分就一定和投影方向垂直。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gram-schmidt",
      "section_id": "orthogonalize",
      "line_id": "orth-1",
      "filename": "orthogonalize-orth-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gram-schmidt/xiaoxiao/orthogonalize-orth-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.55,
      "size": 24768,
      "text": "第一个向量原样保留，作为第一个正交向量。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gram-schmidt",
      "section_id": "orthogonalize",
      "line_id": "orth-2",
      "filename": "orthogonalize-orth-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gram-schmidt/xiaoxiao/orthogonalize-orth-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.37,
      "size": 37872,
      "text": "第二个向量，减去它在第一个向量上的投影，得到与之垂直的新向量。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gram-schmidt",
      "section_id": "orthogonalize",
      "line_id": "orth-3",
      "filename": "orthogonalize-orth-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gram-schmidt/xiaoxiao/orthogonalize-orth-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.47,
      "size": 39456,
      "text": "后面每个向量，都减去它在前面所有正交向量上的投影，依次垂直。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gram-schmidt",
      "section_id": "normalize",
      "line_id": "norm-1",
      "filename": "normalize-norm-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gram-schmidt/xiaoxiao/normalize-norm-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "现在这组向量已经两两垂直，但长度还各不相同。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gram-schmidt",
      "section_id": "normalize",
      "line_id": "norm-2",
      "filename": "normalize-norm-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gram-schmidt/xiaoxiao/normalize-norm-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38016,
      "text": "把每个向量除以自己的模长，长度都变成一，就得到了标准正交基。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gram-schmidt",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gram-schmidt/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.49,
      "size": 39888,
      "text": "换一组输入向量，看红色的投影和绿色的正交结果如何随之变化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gram-schmidt",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gram-schmidt/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.04,
      "size": 32688,
      "text": "不管起点多么歪斜，最终两条基总是严丝合缝地垂直。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gram-schmidt",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gram-schmidt/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "施密特正交化靠减去投影，把歪斜的基一步步扶正。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gram-schmidt",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gram-schmidt/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.0,
      "size": 31968,
      "text": "再单位化，就得到互相垂直、长度为一的标准正交基。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gram-schmidt",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gram-schmidt/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "它是最小二乘、QR 分解等许多方法的基石，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 36.77,
  "total_size": 588240
}